{
  "stem": "12494.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] To us it was, you know, quite a trauma to have to say goodbye to these people who really didn't know what they were doing when they simply put down something on a piece of paper saying Romania instead of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Anyway, next morning we-- we collected the luggage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We went on the trucks to this railroad siding, which was sort of an elliptical elevation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the trains could come from either side and stop, and then you could just walk into the trains.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were-- we were kind of curious what kind of trains would-- would these be, because we weren't sure whether we'd go to Auschwitz or whether we'd go to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were there, the 30 of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we said, as soon as we see the train, we'll know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because if it is a train for people, that is a car-- person cars, passenger cars, then we know we go to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "If it's cattle cars, like the ones on which we came, then we know we go to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Well, there was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So we spread the luggage along the lengths of the siding.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "About one third-- the siding was, say, one unit long, 100 meters long.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Around 30 meters from one end, there was a shed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And on the shed there was a sign saying in German that it's forbidden to go beyond this point.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There wasn't anybody there, so I went beyond that, and I was caught by an SS man who started beating me with his gun, and I lost consciousness.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I woke up in the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And-- and I never recovered from the back injury that I-- I received there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Regular passenger trains, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All those regular deportation trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
